3229,"uid":219147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"港鐵、武裝警察﻿<br />\n合謀恐怖襲擊﻿<br />\n==================﻿<br />\n繼元朗 7.21 黑社會車站恐襲之後，昨晚 8.31 在旺角、太子、油麻地站上演了「港鐵恐襲 2.0｣，恐怖程度遠超 7.21。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n事源 8.31 晚有有反抗爭人士以武器襲擊抗爭者，引發連串衝突。後來港鐵容許大批武裝警察衝入旺角站月台，開始無差別追打無辜市民，當中有情緒失控的武裝警察甚至衝入車廂亂棍施襲！後來有武裝警察發現原來車廂內有記者採訪，才停止襲擊離開車廂。襲擊過後車廂內一片狼藉，有人抱頭痛哭，有人血流披面，受傷人士甚至包括無辜兒童。武裝警察做的不是驅散或拘捕，而是純粹的對市民作出暴力發洩。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n8.31 恐襲比 7.21 更恐怖，原因是施襲者身穿全副武裝，並受到制度的保護，比起黑社會，市民更無法抵抗有系統而且擁有壓倒性力量的暴力行為。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n香港正面對嚴峻的人道危機。我們呼籲國際社會關注並全力支援香港的抗爭者。﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmrOQ9Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmrOQ9Q.png&h=67909333&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baae62c01ace75c5b9c214c1ba1034897e8dab94","tid":1523229,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd6de2adbddeb885f1163fa7ac30b1159fec58ad","tid":1523229,"uid":219147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"831浩劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/371653272981177/posts/1821761524637004?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F371653272981177%2Fposts%2F1821761524637004%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60Cxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=c217a2a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/371653272981177/posts/1821761524637004?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e362d5797df9daeeca4c63a6b65c4950d86c4b75","tid":1523229,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dFMoi1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdFMoi1d.png&h=8dc37308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2136822073313759/posts/2323661137963184?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http